        {
            "title": "A股疲弱   晶片股下挫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日偏軟，晶片股跌，華虹挫一成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日報3343，點或0.26%，今早開報3350，跌2點0.06%，早段見3351點，跌1點或0.03%，即反覆向下，約11:AM見3335，跌17點或0.51%，為上午低位。半日成交3044.5億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報10112點，跌85點或0.84%，今早開報10190，跌7點或0.07%，最高報10190，跌7點或0.07%，即拾級而下，最低報10087，跌110點或1.08%﹐為上午低位，半日成交4835.33億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日報3843點，跌8點或0.23%，今早開報3848，跌4點或0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日跌20點或1%，報2009點，今早開報2028，跌1點或0.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股跌，華虹半導體(688347.SH)挫10.58%，報46.5元 ; 中芯(688981.SH)跌4.37%，報86.05元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14915049-a%e8%82%a1%e7%96%b2%e5%bc%b1-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8b%e6%8c%ab",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 11:41:06",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國4 月出口按年升8.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國4月出口按美元計按年升8.1%，進口跌0.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_CH_Tariffs_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_CH_Tariffs_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以人民幣計算，4月份出口增長9.3%，至2.27萬億元人民幣；進口增長0.8%，至1.57萬億元，貨物貿易進出口總值3.84萬億元，增長5.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">前4個月貨物貿易進出口總值14.14萬億元人民幣，增長2.4%。其中，出口8.39萬億元，增長7.5%；進口5.75萬億元，下降4.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914981-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b4-%e6%9c%88%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%878-1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250414_FI_source-ap_China_Economy-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 11:20:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美亞控股復牌瀉逾61%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美亞控股(Mayer Holdings , 01116)停牌年半後今日復牌，最多曾瀉61.18%，見0.33元，現報0.485元，插42.94%，成交866萬元。   </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250509_fi_01116_mayer_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/768x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250509_fi_01116_mayer_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美亞自2023年9月29日上午九時正起暫停於聯交所買賣，公司昨公布達成所有復牌指引，主要包括刊發所有尚未公布的財務業績，並處理任何審計修改；及對一些指稱進行適當的獨立調查，評估對公司業務營運及財務狀況的影響，公布調查結果並採取適當的補救措施。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司2023年6 月中公布，接獲匿名投訴，提出4 項指稱，包括控制人操縱股份交易 ; 控制人挪用公司資金2.05億元自用 ; 控制人拖欠一家公司的借款，其後由於缺乏資金，導致公司附屬所持的更新項目進度延誤 ; 及董事和公司秘書罊意拖延召開董事會。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914862-%e7%be%8e%e4%ba%9e%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c%e7%80%89%e9%80%be61",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250509_fi_01116_mayer_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 11:10:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬上阿姨曾挫11%  鈞達回吐逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬上阿姨(02589)今早股價回落，一度低見140元，挫11.62%，新造146元，瀉7.83%，成交3820萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬上阿姨昨日掛牌急升40.93%，報158.4元，全日均高於招股價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股仍高於招股價113.12元，現比招股價高29.07%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鈞達新能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鈞達新能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鈞達新能源官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一新股鈞達新能源(02865)現挫5.64%，報25.1元，最低見24.5元，昨收報26.6元，較招股價22.15元升 20.09%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914728-%e6%bb%ac%e4%b8%8a%e9%98%bf%e5%a7%a8%e6%9b%be%e6%8c%ab11-%e9%88%9e%e9%81%94%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/Jenny-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 10:10:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新地SIERRA SEA 1B期首推160伙  平均呎價高2.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14912778&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新地(00016)發展的西貢十四鄉西沙灣發展項目的SIERRA SEA第1B期公布首張價單，折實平均呎價10638元，較SIERRA SEA第1A(2)期上月公布的首批折實平均呎價略高2.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">SIERRA SEA 第1A(2)期累售755伙，套現逾40億元。第1B期今天公布首張價單，提供160伙，折實平均呎價10638元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">SIERRA SEA第1B期首張價單包括7間1房、128間2房及25間3房戶，實用面積302至807方呎，付款方式與第1A期相若，維持最高樓價15%折扣，折實售價300.05萬至935.76萬元，折實呎價9499至11695元。入場單位為Bleu Avenue第3座G2樓J室，實用面積302方呎，折實售價300.05萬元，折實呎價9935元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14912778-%e6%96%b0%e5%9c%b0sierra-sea-1b%e6%9c%9f%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%a8160%e4%bc%99-%e5%b9%b3%e5%9d%87%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%982-3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_new-flats_bp_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 10:01:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息連續3天全線跌  H按按息2年內首低於封頂息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14912279&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元同業拆息連續3 天全線下跌，隔夜息較上日的2.49905厘跌210.95基點，1個月拆息跌破3 厘，報2.09452厘，較昨天的3.08厘跌98.55基點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240222_FI_source_licensed_HK-bank_704.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240222_FI_source_licensed_HK-bank_704.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">1周拆息報1.18095厘，跌160.92基點 ; 3個月拆息2.77036厘，跌61.25基點 ; 6個月拆息3.13667厘，跌33.91基點。1 年拆息3.35345厘跌25.58基點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以H按H+1.3 厘計，息率為3.3945厘，低於現在的封頂息3.5厘(P-1.75厘)，約兩年以來首次低於封頂利率。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以貸款400萬元，還款期25年計，每月還款額19790元，以封頂息3.5厘計，則為20025元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14912279-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e9%80%a3%e7%ba%8c3%e5%a4%a9%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e8%b7%8c-h%e6%8c%89%e6%8c%89%e6%81%af2%e5%b9%b4%e5%85%a7%e9%a6%96%e4%bd%8e%e6%96%bc%e5%b0%81%e9%a0%82%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241016_FI_HK-BANK_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 10:01:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大埔康樂園單號屋1580萬元沽   8年蝕2成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14911865&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產大埔康樂園分行稱，大埔康樂園最新錄21街單號屋成交，單位建築面積1850平方呎，實用面積1237平方呎，叫價約1780萬元，日前議價後以1580萬元沽出，實用平均呎價約14254元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據了解，新買家為外區客，原業主於2017年以1990萬元購入單位，持貨約8年，現轉手賬面蝕約410萬元離場，單位期內貶值約20.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14911865-%e5%a4%a7%e5%9f%94%e5%ba%b7%e6%a8%82%e5%9c%92%e5%96%ae%e8%99%9f%e5%b1%8b1580%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%b2%bd-8%e5%b9%b4%e8%9d%952%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 10:01:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "比特幣破10萬美元關   虛擬貨幣幾全線升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比特幣在3 個月破10萬美元大關，據Coindesk報價，24小時內最高位見10.364萬美元，最低報97777美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比特幣現報10.29萬美元，升5.13%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250308_CH_Crypto_Bitcoin_Prices_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250308_CH_Crypto_Bitcoin_Prices_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他虛擬貨幣也升，以太幣升20.57%，報2196.01美元，最高見2227.54美元。瑞波幣(XRP)升7.88%，報2.3070美元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">幣安幣(BNB)升3.95%，報625.05美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14914705-%e6%af%94%e7%89%b9%e5%b9%a3%e7%a0%b410%e8%90%ac%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%97%9c-%e8%99%9b%e6%93%ac%e8%b2%a8%e5%b9%a3%e5%b9%be%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e5%8d%87",
